Here we wil do basic linux command with help of anisbile to create a file from master server to slave server.

1. Create a inventory file and under inventory file place the IP of slave servers.
2. we can run below command :

ansible -i inventory all -m "shell" -a "touch filename"

this will create a file in slave server.

Here for using adhoc ansible command, we are using ansible
-m denotes mode
all denotes all content in inventory file means all server mentioned in that file
